  "content": "\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"hiq-page-wrap\">\r\n<div class=\"hiq-t-wrap\">\r\n\t\t\r\n  \t  <div class=\"hiq-t \">\r\n\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"breadcrumbs\"><li><a class=\"breadcrumb-links\" hqid=\"1788908\"  href=\"/home\">Home</a></li> <li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"3500940\" href=\"/omni\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">Manhattan Active® Omni</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"2158742\" href=\"/customer-engagement-3\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">Customer Engagement</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"2164765\" href=\"/ui-help-3\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">UI Help</a></li><li><span>&rsaquo;&rsaquo;</span><a hqid=\"2182246\" href=\"/customer-management\" class=\"breadcrumb-links\">Customer Management</a></li><li> <span>››</span>Customer Management Overview</li></ul>  \t\r\n\t\t<h2>Customer Management</h2>\n\n<p></p>\n\n<p>Customer Management solution helps the Customer Service Representatives (CSR) to maintain customer profiles. It allows the CSR to update customer data based on the permission available with the CSR user role.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>The <a hqid=\"1994571\" href=\"/cusprofile\">Customer Profile</a> module allows the CSR to manage the general information of a registered customer such as the customer&#39;s personal details, contact, shipping/billing address, and payment&nbsp;and preferences methods.</p>\n\n<p>The <a hqid=\"1995114\" href=\"/deactivating-customers\">Deactivate Customer</a> option enables the CSR to deactivate and activate the registered customers.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dzf8vqv24eqhg.cloudfront.net/userfiles/4665/7671/ckfinder/images/CustomerManagement.png?Policy=eyJTdGF0ZW1lbnQiOlt7IlJlc291cmNlIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9kemY4dnF2MjRlcWhnLmNsb3VkZnJvbnQubmV0L3VzZXJmaWxlcy80NjY1Lzc2NzEvY2tmaW5kZXIvaW1hZ2VzL0N1c3RvbWVyTWFuYWdlbWVudC5wbmciLCJDb25kaXRpb24iOnsiRGF0ZUxlc3NUaGFuIjp7IkFXUzpFcG9jaFRpbWUiOjE3NTQ3NTQwMTR9fX1dfQ__&Signature=TEy8XMogjpSrFbfrbOSkITKECKYHjCyQuTNSfPcNWTr2ENsTop38iXOTYkz53